	 <div class="intro">
	<h3 ><center>About</center> </h3>
<div class="card-group">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">&nbsp;Genesis<br></h4>
                <p class="card-text">B.V Jagadeesh Science centre is an institution established by the National Education Society of Karnataka [NES] in the year 2001, for everyone interested in learning science, particularly focused to encourage youth to take up careers in
                    basic sciences.<br><br></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">&nbsp;Objectives<br></h4>
                <p class="card-text">Establish a dynamic destination where families, adults and children can explore science through books, interactive exhibits, live demonstrations, innovative programs and inspirational films.<br></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">&nbsp;Values<br></h4>
                <p class="card-text">We aspire to stimulate curiosity and inspire science learning in everyone, because we value science as an indispensable tool for understanding our world and enriching people's lives.<br></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
